::Killer/Zeus/Ares::

Killer growls, transforming into his raven beast mode and looking at the 
Predacons in front of him. He backs up slightly.

Zeus and Ares transform into beast mode as well. Zeus into an eagle and Ares 
into a ram. Zeus laughs.

"Fools! This will not trap me!" he yells, missile launchers emerging from 
under his wings to fire at the cave entrance.
